message: "Dart new podcast series is produced in collaboration with Truckers Against Trafficking (TAT), the Minnesota Trucking Association (MTA) and the Minnesota Bureau of Criminal Apprehension (MBCA). The five-part series examines how the state of Minnesota and MTA members have been involved in the effort to address human trafficking."

data.description: Dart has a total of 500 company drivers and owner-operators driving within the Dart Network fleet who are certified with Truckers Against Trafficking.
data.title: Dart Transit creates podcast series to help drivers combat human trafficking
